GxRenderers

Class GxRendererGroupCellRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • GxRenderers.GxRendererAbstract
      • GxRenderers.GxRendererGroupCellRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GxRendererInterface

    public class GxRendererGroupCellRenderer
extends GxRendererAbstract
    If you are grouping in the grid, then you will need to provide a group cell renderer as the group cell renderer is what provides the user with the expand and collapse functionality.
    Author:
    Hyyan Abo Fakher
